'''达拉斯第一浸信会'''（First Baptist Dallas）是一个[[美南浸信会|美南浸信会]]的{{link-en|巨型教會|Megachurch|巨型教会}}，位于美国[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[达拉斯|达拉斯]]。它创建于1868年7月30日，到2016年拥有12,000名信徒。<ref name="cnn2011">{{cite web | url= http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/10/07/breaking-pastor-to-gop-dont-vote-for-romney-because-hes-mormon/ | title= Conservative pastor on Romney: Don't vote for a Mormon | work= Political Ticker (blog) | date= 2011-10-07 | publisher= CNN | accessdate= 2011-10-08 | archive-date= 2021-04-22 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210422210721/https://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2011/10/07/breaking-pastor-to-gop-dont-vote-for-romney-because-hes-mormon/ | dead-url= no }}</ref>此外还开办学校和广播电台。

目前的教堂建于1891年。现任牧师罗伯特·杰弗斯曾在讲道中曾批评[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Jillian Rayfield |url=http://tpmmuckraker.talkingpointsmemo.com/2010/09/dallas_pastor_islam_promotes_pedophilia_video.php |title=Dallas Pastor Defends Claim That Islam 'Promotes Pedophilia' |publisher=Talking Points Memo |date=2010-09-07 |accessdate=2011-10-08 |archive-date=2013-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130224054913/http://tpmmuckraker.talkingpointsmemo.com/2010/09/dallas_pastor_islam_promotes_pedophilia_video.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[犹太人|犹太人]]、[[摩门教|摩门教]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Karen Brooks and Peter Bohan |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/09/us-usa-campaign-jeffress-idUSTRE7982DV20111009 |title=Texas pastor stands ground on "cult" comment about Mormons |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=October 9, 2011 |accessdate=2011-10-09 |archive-date=2011-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010023413/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/09/us-usa-campaign-jeffress-idUSTRE7982DV20111009 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Jeffress Says Satan Is Behind Roman Catholicism|url=http://www.rightwingwatch.org/content/jeffress-says-satan-behind-roman-catholicism|publisher=Right Wing Watch|date=2011-10-08|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919020002/http://www.rightwingwatch.org/content/jeffress-says-satan-behind-roman-catholicism|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[同性恋者|同性恋者]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dmagazine.com/Home/D_Magazine/2012/January/The_Savior_Robert_Jeffress_of_First_Baptist_Dallas.aspx |title=The Savior_Robert Jeffress_of First Baptist Dallas |accessdate=2012-02-05 |archive-date=2012-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205113500/http://dmagazine.com/Home/D_Magazine/2012/January/The_Savior_Robert_Jeffress_of_First_Baptist_Dallas.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/football/jets/tebow-cancels-gig-controversial-dallas-church-article-1.1269712#ixzz31br1bf53|title=Tebow cancels gig at controversial Dallas church|publisher=|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930193227/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/football/jets/tebow-cancels-gig-controversial-dallas-church-article-1.1269712#ixzz31br1bf53|dead-url=no}}</ref>，引发争议。

美国传教士[[葛培理|葛培理]]在1953年成为达拉斯第一浸信会的成员。2008年，90岁的葛培理改属南卡罗来纳州斯巴达堡的第一浸信会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://religionblog.dallasnews.com/2008/12/billy-graham-moves-membership.html|title=Billy Graham moves membership from First Baptist Dallas|publisher=''Dallas News''|date=2008-12-29|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830035216/http://religionblog.dallasnews.com/2008/12/billy-graham-moves-membership.html/|archive-date=2016-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

